32
00:02:02,279 --> 00:02:06,999
On the seventh day, following the Lord’s
instructions, Joshua has the army march around

33
00:02:06,999 --> 00:02:13,379
the city seven times and on the seventh circuit
he has the trumpets sound and the army shout

34
