84
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:38,020
Bride or harlot covered in filth? ... both?

85
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:42,150
Some cities in the Bible are often classed
as places of sin -- Sodom and Gomorrah being

86
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:46,520
the most obvious example -- but let’s not
forget: cities also provide opportunities

87
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:48,639
for humankind to unite.

88
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:52,360
