107
00:07:09,050 --> 00:07:15,099
It’s his son who settles at Alba Longa,
and a later descendant–Romulus–who builds

108
00:07:15,099 --> 00:07:17,020
the city of seven hills.

109
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:22,159
But hold the mythical phone for just a moment...
who is this “Romulus”?

110
00:07:22,159 --> 00:07:26,449
The story of Romulus and his twin brother
Remus begins in Alba Longa where a woman named

111
00:07:26,449 --> 00:07:28,480
