132
00:08:48,610 --> 00:08:53,410
place for a new city, but they can’t agree
on the exact location.

133
00:08:53,410 --> 00:08:59,111
Romulus receives a sign from the gods telling
him to choose the Palatine hill as the site,

134
00:08:59,111 --> 00:09:02,630
so he sets out to mark the boundaries by digging
