144
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:36,570
So Romulus has a spot for his city and no
rival twin, but he still has one big problem:

145
00:09:36,570 --> 00:09:37,570
not enough people.

146
00:09:37,570 --> 00:09:42,810
So he puts out the word that the hill will
be a refuge for the criminals and runaways

147
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:43,970
of Italy.

148
00:09:43,970 --> 00:09:46,200
And that’s exactly who shows up.

149
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:53,040
